{"tid":288929,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"90後情侶創業 !八間店! 營業額2000萬 !","createTime":"2017-06-18T14:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T16:52:26.000Z","uid":74796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e862dc281199be035d67fcc7ba5b3620774c9cf2","tid":288929,"uid":74796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1834064/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1834064%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=sSr05TO93aEjf9NEZClhm5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=52e0fb01\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1834064/?r=mcsdfb</a><img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1830000/1834064/90_thumb_20170613_c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1830000%2F1834064%2F90_thumb_20170613_c_1024.jpg&h=05ac23f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十多歲的你可能剛步出校門，或已在社會工作好幾年，仍尋尋覓覓人生方向。90後情侶Alan(伍卓倫)、Zoe(黃俊然)在二十歲剛出頭時，選擇創業，2010年開設首間設計公司，至今已擁有8間店舖及公司，每年營業額達1,500萬元至2,000萬元，盈利約700萬元。<br />\n<br />\n現在26歲的Alan，中學在新西蘭讀書，畢業後原本計劃上大學，但自小數口精的他想到學費連生活高達100萬元，計過當大學畢業後，倘若每月人工約1萬元，要用8年多時間才可賺回百萬元，感覺不太化算，故決定回港工作，寧可用幾年時間建立人脈關係再創業，他深信一樣有好出路。<br />\n<br />\nAlan回港後認識了Zoe，當時她在大學修讀設計，同時兼做freelance設計師，二人於2010年合作開首間設計公司。<br />\n<br />\n由於部分店舖如Lasermads及Combo都有不同的設備的儀器，故需動用大量資金，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">前者的投資額便要150萬元，當時二人決定引入其他股東合資，最終合共有13個股東。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nAlan說雖然股東多意見多，但優點更多，除可減低投資風險外，更有助生意發展。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/9e/%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E9%9C%80%E7%88%B6%E5%B9%B9.jpeg/revision/latest?cb=20120818102448\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F9e%2F%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E9%259C%2580%25E7%2588%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B9.jpeg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120818102448&h=344a28bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位廢青學到野未?"},{"pid":"463cc6b9cc67f22396f2a21e24ec1ed9203c0528","tid":288929,"uid":18430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"乜背景資料都冇仲想批鬥人 比啲誠意ok?"},{"pid":"c8646ec3767b150524723f7f26eee1bf984e2010","tid":288929,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"每人十零萬應該唔洗父幹啦"}]}